  "response": "Here are some tips for success in college:\n\n1. Academic Advice\n- Attend classes regularly\n- Take good notes\n- Manage your time effectively\n- Stay organized\n- Study consistently\n- Seek help when needed\n- Get to know your professors\n\n2. Social Tips\n- Be open to meeting new people\n- Join clubs and organizations\n- Balance social life and academics\n- Be respectful to others\n- Practice good communication skills\n\n3. Personal Development\n- Take care of your health\n- Learn to budget\n- Develop good sleep habits\n- Exercise regularly\n- Practice self-discipline\n- Set personal and academic goals\n\n4. Practical Considerations\n- Get involved on campus\n- Learn to do laundry and basic life skills\n- Network with peers and professors\n- Consider internships\n- Explore career opportunities\n- Be responsible and independent\n\n5. Mental Health\n- Manage stress\n- Seek counseling if needed\n- Maintain a support system\n- Be kind to yourself\n- Practice self-care\n\n6. Financial Advice\n- Apply for scholarships\n- Create a budget\n- Use student discounts\n- Consider part-time work\n- Be mindful of student loans\n\nRemember, college is about learning, growing, and preparing for your future.",
